# Jiggon Algorithm: High Volatility Scalper
# Looks for explosive, volatile market conditions. 
# Only triggers when ATR is heavily elevated, attempting to catch massive candles.

IF ATR > 2.0 AND RSI > 60 AND EMA_TREND == BULLISH THEN BUY
IF ATR > 2.0 AND RSI < 40 AND EMA_TREND == BEARISH THEN SELL
